name: Fauna Flowers 07 - Piranha Flower
description:
It is a tiny, aggressive and voracious flower. It's never alone. Where there's one... there's a bunch. Its field is the most dangerous spot in the forest. No animal is able to cross the Piranha garden and walk away alive. The perfect gift for your mother-in-law.

Fauna Flowers is a collection made of animals mixed with plants in a new kind of magical possibilities. Discover this world where flowers can be a magnificent diversity of beautiful and unique creatures.
